{
  "id": "69ec2001258cbbd4e8c18223",
  "title": "言葉を倍にするやつ",
  "created": 1777082375,
  "updated": 1777121325,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ec2001258cbbd4e8c18223",
      "text": "言葉を倍にするやつ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082375,
      "updated": 1777082376
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec27970000000000745408",
      "text": " 文中(単語中)の言葉を倍にして別の意味を作る[言葉遊び]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084312,
      "updated": 1777084382
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec27a7000000000074540b",
      "text": " 卑猥になると楽しい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084328,
      "updated": 1777085105
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec20080000000000c88fa8",
      "text": " >[https://x.com/mukai_rinjin/status/2047603999868915766?s=46&t=gkSZtjGEtUZPO0JCzBxCBw @mukai_rinjin]: 言葉を倍にするヤツ、「腑に落ちん」→「ふにふにお○んちん」が好き",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777082376,
      "updated": 1777084313
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec27940000000000745407",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084308,
      "updated": 1777084308
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec200b0000000000c88fa9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082380,
      "updated": 1777082380
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21a40000000000c88faa",
      "text": "　腑に落ちん→ふにふにおちんちん",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777082789,
      "updated": 1777121325
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21a70000000000c88fac",
      "text": "　賃金",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082791,
      "updated": 1777082796
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21ac0000000000c88fad",
      "text": "　ワクチン→ワクワクちんちん",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777082796,
      "updated": 1777121319
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21ae0000000000c88fae",
      "text": "　ワクチン接種",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082799,
      "updated": 1777082807
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21b70000000000c88faf",
      "text": "　珍道中",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082808,
      "updated": 1777082834
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21d20000000000c88fb0",
      "text": "　チンパンジー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082834,
      "updated": 1777082844
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21e90000000000c88fb1",
      "text": "　メキシコ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082857,
      "updated": 1777082859
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21eb0000000000c88fb2",
      "text": "　なでしこジャパン",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082860,
      "updated": 1777082865
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec22050000000000c88fb3",
      "text": "　無知の知",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082885,
      "updated": 1777082892
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec22130000000000c88fb4",
      "text": "　チンギスハーン",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777082899,
      "updated": 1777082904
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec21a40000000000c88fab",
      "text": "\tパイの実",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777082789,
      "updated": 1777096789
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec2801000000000074540c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084418,
      "updated": 1777084418
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec28470000000000745412",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084488,
      "updated": 1777084488
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec28480000000000745413",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084489,
      "updated": 1777084489
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec2807000000000074540f",
      "text": "中国語で倍にして言うとき",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084424,
      "updated": 1777085198
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec28b5000000000074541b",
      "text": " https://chu-gokugo.com/2020/08/27/中国名前繰り返し/",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777085198,
      "updated": 1777085198
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec29ed0000000000745423",
      "text": " 同じ音がつくと可愛らしい意味になる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084910,
      "updated": 1777084927
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec2ab80000000000745425",
      "text": "  日本語の〇〇ちゃんみたいになる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777085113,
      "updated": 1777085131
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec2acb0000000000745426",
      "text": "  中国語で〇〇ちゃんと呼ぶ言い方は[小猫](シャオマオ)とかもあるな[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777085131,
      "updated": 1777085200
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec28b30000000000745417",
      "text": " 一文字の名前を愛称として呼ぶときに同じ音を二回繰り返す",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084595,
      "updated": 1777084820
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec29fc0000000000745424",
      "text": "  名前が「玲」の人を「玲ちゃん」という意味で「玲玲(リンリン)」と呼ぶ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084924,
      "updated": 1777085252
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec2994000000000074541e",
      "text": " 二回繰り返す名前が正式についてる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084820,
      "updated": 1777084940
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec29b90000000000745420",
      "text": "  パンダの名前がこれかな？[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084857,
      "updated": 1777084950
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec29a6000000000074541f",
      "text": "  薬屋のひとりごとの[猫猫]もこれかな？[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084839,
      "updated": 1777084856
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec2989000000000074541d",
      "text": " 本名でない[幼少名](子供の頃だけに使うニックネーム)で呼んでる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084810,
      "updated": 1777084989
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec29d70000000000745422",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777084888,
      "updated": 1777084888
    }
  ]
}